er-secondary bg-cover bg-center bg-trust-security"></div><div class="px-6 py-5 max-md:py-4"><h3 class="mb-2 heading-lg font-bold">Security</h3><p class="text-sm text-secondary">Expo is committed to keeping your data secure. We use a variety of industry-standard technologies and services to secure your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, use, and loss.</p></div></div><div class="border border-secondary bg-default shadow-xs overflow-hidden rounded-lg"><div class="min-h-43.75 border-b border-secondary bg-cover bg-center bg-trust-compliance"></div><div class="px-6 py-5 max-md:py-4"><h3 class="mb-2 heading-lg font-bold">SOC 2 Compliance</h3><p class="text-sm text-secondary">Expo is committed to enterprise-grade security and has obtained SOC 2 Type 2 attestation.<br/><br/><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-link transition-opacity hocus:opacity-80" href="https://app.drata.com/trust/9cc346b0-0c38-11ee-865f-029d78a187d9">Request a copy of our latest SOC 2 Type 2 report</a></p></div></div><div class="border border-secondary bg-default shadow-xs overflow-hidden rounded-lg"><div class="min-h-43.75 border-b border-secondary bg-cover bg-center bg-trust-privacy"></div><div class="px-6 py-5 max-md:py-4"><h3 class="mb-2 heading-lg font-bold">Privacy</h3><p class="text-sm text-secondary">In all scenarios regarding our users&#x27; data, Expo is GDPR-, CCPA-, and Data Privacy Framework-compliant.<br/><br/><a class="text-link transition-opacity hocus:opacity-80" href="https://expo.dev/privacy-explained">Learn more about privacy at Expo</a></p></div></div><div class="border border-secondary bg-default shadow-xs overflow-hidden rounded-lg"><div class="min-h-43.75 border-b border-secondary bg-cover bg-center bg-trust-enterprise"></div><div class="px-6 py-5 max-md:py-4"><h3 class="mb-2 heading-lg font-bold">Enterprise</h3><p class="text-sm text-secondary">We&#x27;re ready to work with you to get Expo onboarded with your enterprise. MSA and DPA terms are available.<br/><br/><a class="text-link transition-opacity hocus:opacity-80">Contact our team to get started</a></p></div></div></div><h2 class="w-full heading-2xl font-bold">Data security and privacy</h2><div class="my-4 grid w-full grid-cols-2 gap-x-24 gap-y-12 max-md:mt-2 max-md:grid-cols-1"><div class="flex flex-col gap-3"><div class="flex content-center items-center rounded-md w-fit border border-secondary bg-default p-2.5 shadow-xs dark:bg-screen"><svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" class="text-icon-default translate-z shrink-0 icon-lg" role="img"><g id="users-01-outline-icon"><path id="Icon" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M22 21V19C22 17.1362 20.7252 15.5701 19 15.126M15.5 3.29076C16.9659 3.88415 18 5.32131 18 7C18 8.67869 16.9659 10.1159 15.5 10.7092M17 21C17 19.1362 17 18.2044 16.6955 17.4693C16.2895 16.4892 15.5108 15.7105 14.5307 15.3045C13.7956 15 12.8638 15 11 15H8C6.13623 15 5.20435 15 4.46927 15.3045C3.48915 15.7105 2.71046 16.4892 2.30448 17.4693C2 18.2044 2 19.1362 2 21M13.5 7C13.5 9.20914 11.7091 11 9.5 11C7.29086 11 5.5 9.20914 5.5 7C5.5 4.79086 7.29086 3 9.5 3C11.7091 3 13.5 4.79086 13.5 7Z"></path></g></svg></div><h3 class="heading-lg font-bold">End-user data</h3><p class="text-sm text-secondary">Expo Application Services involve building and distributing your application code, not your application data. Thus, Expo is not aware of your users&#x27; identities and does not store or handle PII related to your users. You can read more about the data we collect and how we handle it in our<!-- --> <a class="text-link transition-opacity hocus:opacity-80" href="/privacy-explained">Privacy Explained document</a>.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-3"><div class="flex content-center items-center rounded-md w-fit border border-secondary bg-default p-2.5 shadow-xs dark:bg-screen"><svg fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" class="text-icon-default translate-z shrink-0 icon-lg" role="img">